high_descs: Turn left and go forward toward the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the glass from the sink.
Turn around and move forward, turn right at the oven, then look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the glass inside, heat it up, then take it out.
Go to the upper cabinet directly to your right.
Open the cabinet, put the glass inside, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm glass in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right to face the sink.

Turn around, go forward, turn right to face the oven, go forward to the oven.
Heat the glass in the microwave above the oven.
Go to the counter to the right of the oven.
Put the glass on the left side of the cabinet above the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot glass in a cabinet.
